itial test from 1 March was negative, the subsequent retest on 3 March has been clearly positive. She is isolated at [[Bulovka Hospital]] together with another woman that travelled in the group with the American and Ecuadorian. The tests of the third woman have been negative so far.\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''6'''<ref name=case6a>{{cite web|url=https://www.idnes.cz/zpravy/domaci/koronavirus-praha-matka-dite-zakladni-skola.A200304_091442_domaci_remy|title=Matce v Praze odhalila koronavirus soukrom\u00e1 klinika. \u0160kol\u00e1ci jsou v izolaci \u2013 idnes.cz|website=Mlad\u00e1 fronta DNES|language=cs |access-date=4 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 4 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}}\n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Passo del Tonale]]<ref name=CZ.case9-12>{{cite web|url=https://www.idnes.cz/zpravy/domaci/koronavirus.A200305_142537_domaci_remy|title=Po\u010det naka\u017een\u00fdch koronavirem stoupl na 12, mezi nimi mu\u017e a d\u00edt\u011b z Prahy|website=mzcr.cz|access-date=5 March 2020}}</ref>\n| [[Prague]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Female\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A mother of two from Prague 6 developed symptoms after visiting [[Passo del Tonale]] in [[Trentino]] region in Italy. The woman has been tested for coronavirus at an undisclosed private clinic. The positive result was unofficial, but in the afternoon it was confirmed by the Czech National Reference Laboratory. The woman is in quarantine at [[Bulovka Hospital]] and her family is self-quarantined at home.<ref name=case6b>{{cite web|url=https://www.novinky.cz/zahranicni/koronavirus/clanek/primator-hrib-predbehl-hygieniky-ministra-i-premiera-a-ohlasil-novy-nepotvrzeny-pripad-koronaviru-40315472|title=Prim\u00e1tor H\u0159ib p\u0159edb\u011bhl hygieniky, ministra i premi\u00e9ra a ohl\u00e1sil nov\u00fd, ov\u0161em nepotvrzen\u00fd, p\u0159\u00edpad koronaviru |website=novinky.cz |lang